<div class="nbunit" id="7May1932"><font color="red">7 May 1932</font> <i>BLHW</i> (to Harriet Weaver): As for W i P I cannot continue it for the moment &hellip; Not being allowed to do any work I put James Stephens&apos;s poem on the wind into French, Italian, German, Latin and Norwegian </div>
